data.description: Check out the most charming cottage River Rocks Plantation has to offer. Enjoy the elegance of marble countertops, custom cabinetry, KitchenAid appliances, tile surround showers, walk-in closets, wide plank White Oak floors, brick floors, 12’ ceilings and a beautiful Pecky Cypress ceiling in the foyer. Relax in the screened loggia or the fenced yard overlooking Lake Guntersville. A cozy retreat with a perfect blend of style and comfort. This property is conveniently located to the pool and Gathering House. You don’t want to miss this one!
